{"tid":228372,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好困擾","createTime":"2017-05-03T22:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T23:11:19.000Z","uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff98ca4f1b987b6590cb86b8cff59177b4c0e91","tid":228372,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:11:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得屋企好多隻眼望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係冇見過佢地 不過我好驚<br />\n佢地無處不在 以前已經搵過高人消滅佢地<br />\n但係佢地最後都會返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由一變到三 數量不斷增加<br />\n我唔係冇努力過克服 同佢地同居<br />\n但係佢地越黎越過份<br />\n只要我熄左燈唔夠一個鐘 佢地就出黎<br />\n我每行一步都要好小心 我好驚撞到佢地<br />\n最後，我屌哂你班小強老母 人地屋企垃圾崗<br />\n我屋企咁撚整齊又高 點解你班仆街係都要入我間屋<br />\n冇野食架屌你老母"},{"pid":"41e39acc0012840796833a88ff5ddc511c17893e","tid":228372,"uid":65268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:13:18.000Z","msg":"廚房一見到兜野熱水比佢感受下人性既光輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f3546d5a5630a957a84e0328209e437828c96b","tid":228372,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廚房一見到兜野熱水比佢感受下人性既光輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係冇努力過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rm305C8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRm305C8.jpg&h=ae349056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我滅左佢一個兄弟 點知班仆街 一隻係個櫃邊爬出黎 一隻係吸塵機行過"},{"pid":"54bdb2469ff1f400e300159aed68fb98d82d317a","tid":228372,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:17:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04b00dcf0dfcdf01d3c2056216683e1bcc574184","tid":228372,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渣ga 屋企幾年冇見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明已經有人日日抹 所有野都封好 點解有甲由 已經冇野食"},{"pid":"d1e157401a66316ecd15fd97d89f20e