ockquote><br />\n佢地識講野架,你試下同佢地say 個hi<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地好串,唔係咁鐘意應人<br />\n<br />\n你逐隻say hi, 應該有1,2隻nice d 會應你機</blockquote><br />\n我應承過師父唔殺甲由 但係你地一定要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e728a14245c2aab88cbfc5382cd5f9a7eb4b65dd","tid":228372,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c7a672038463e960d547d8704ca7b7b4e2b47c6","tid":228372,"uid":71322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T22:49:48.000Z","msg":"試下搬屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb9216a6cde89f0bea09c591ad2bdb47e861a05","tid":228372,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T23:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你地估甲由生存左幾多年 會唔會識字 我諗住貼個時間表係到</blockquote><br />\n佢地識講野架,你試下同佢地say 個hi<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地好串,唔係咁鐘意應人<br />\n<br />\n你逐隻say hi, 應該有1,2隻nice d 會應你機</blockquote><br />\n我應承過師父唔殺甲由 但係你地一定要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你上邊張圖先話消滅左人地一個兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔肯道歉 而我都係無心之失"}]}